steps.html_instructions: Head south on S 3rd St toward E State St
Turn right to merge onto I-70 W/I-71 S

Keep left at the fork to continue on I-71 S, follow signs for Cincinnati/OH-315 N
Entering Kentucky
Keep right at the fork to stay on I-71 S, follow signs for Louisville
Take exit 5 on the left for I-264/Watterson Expy
Exit 5 turns slightly left and becomes I-264 W
Take exit 12 for I-65 N/KY-61/I-65 S toward Indianapolis/Nashville
Keep left, follow signs for I-65 S/Nashville/I-65 N/Downtown/Louisville/Indianapolis

Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-65 S/Nashville and merge onto I-65 S
Entering Tennessee
Keep right at the fork to stay on I-65 S, follow signs for I-40 W/Huntsville/Memphis
Take exit 84B on the left to merge onto I-40 W toward Memphis
Keep left to stay on I-40 W
Take exit 10B for I-40 W toward Little Rock
Exit 10B turns slightly right and becomes I-40 W

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-40 W, follow signs for Interstate 40 W/Little Rock
Entering Arkansas
Keep left at the fork to stay on I-40 W, follow signs for Little Rock
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-30 W
Take exit 139B for I-630
Continue onto I-630 W
Take exit 2B for Doctor Martin Luther King Junior Drive

Turn right onto Dr Martin Luther King Dr/M L King (signs for State Capitol Complex)
Continue to follow Dr Martin Luther King Dr
Turn left onto W 7th St
Turn right onto State Capitol
Slight right to stay on State Capitol
